{
  "stem": "27409.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they had to leave on the 20-- on the 26th, if I [INAUDIBLE]. 26th or 27th. 26th, we had to leave Burgas, and being a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to leave at 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "To leave the [INAUDIBLE] waters of Burgas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had to bring-- mine was the last transfer to arrive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Had some incidents with the train because some religious didn't want to go on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they paid, [NON-ENGLISH], the station commander where we stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we went on and on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We arrived in time in Burgas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Went on the boat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There, again, I was in leadership.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "These were Italian, Spanish, sailors, under Jewish command, former American Navy officers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And Israeli, because Israel was already on the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We came to the Dardanelles, again, under pressure of the British we were stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This is our [INAUDIBLE], and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But, again, their Jewish representative, which paid, again, [INAUDIBLE] of our holy days [? at ?] people, and to pass at Dardanelle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "As we came out from the Aegean Sea, we were surrounded, first caught by the fleet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "First, two planes appeared [INAUDIBLE], and then 13 warships surrounded us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Two submarines surrounded us and asked us to give in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We said we [INAUDIBLE] the ships-- let the ships sink.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We agreed not to go to Tobruk as they wanted, the British fleet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was open sea, without permit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were under Panamanian flag, and we were caught and surrounded, put it blue white flag up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were brought on the 1st of January to Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Near Famagusta in Caraolos, the so-called summer camp, which already had five camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We brought-- part went to Caraolos, part went to the winter camp in Dekhelia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There I started, again, working, organizing the groups and this other small military part.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
